WEBVTT

00:02.036 --> 00:05.705
For most of my life Libya
was a word with bad

00:05.705 --> 00:06.107
associations.

00:06.108 --> 00:09.142
Libya meant Gaddafi.

00:09.143 --> 00:09.743
Libya meant terrorism.

00:09.744 --> 00:14.414
Pan am flight 103 went down
in a blazing fireball.

00:14.415 --> 00:18.017
Libya, a bad place where a
comical dictator was the

00:18.018 --> 00:18.386
absolute power.

00:18.387 --> 00:22.255
Nobody in Libya,
however, was laughing.

00:22.256 --> 00:23.690
Reports of explosions.

00:23.691 --> 00:25.492
Clashes between rioters
and security forces.

00:25.493 --> 00:29.462
In 2011, what was previously
unthinkable happened.

00:29.463 --> 00:31.464
The Libyan people Rose up and

00:31.465 --> 00:32.465
fought for their freedom.

00:32.466 --> 00:36.769
Heavy battles raging
around the Libyan capital.

00:36.770 --> 00:44.311
They fought like hell, the
rebels are about to force

00:44.312 --> 00:45.612
Gaddafi's complete departure.

00:45.613 --> 00:49.382
They recorded the whole
thing on their cell phones.

00:49.383 --> 00:52.886
Libya!

00:53.821 --> 01:01.821
♪

